data.description:
Welcome to your private escape! Beautiful craftsmanship and attention to detail on this fully remodeled home with an impressive list of improvements. Very spacious open floor plan four bedroom/two bath home with detached two car garage situated nicely on over five acres, close to BLM with plenty of room to make your own with expansions or additions. All new windows, new interior & exterior doors, new premium paint throughout entire interior and exterior, custom shaker cabinets throughout, quartz countertops, new stainless steel appliances, all new plumbing fixtures, new AC & furnace coil, new carpet in all bedrooms, premium flooring in traffic areas & bathrooms, new garage door opener, all new interior & exterior light fixtures...the list goes on and on. Come take a look and let your imagination go from there!
For a video tour go to:
https://youtu.be/54FG0z4kaPl
